column5: GOT OUT YESTERDAY  AND ABSOLUTELY DESTROYED THEM. OVER 40FISH BETWEEN 2 OF US. GOT OUT TODAY AFTER THE RAINS.DIDNT DO MUCH BUT DIRTY UP WATER SOME. GOT 8 OUT OF 4 TRIBS TODAY. ODD THING FOR TODAY WAS SEEING 2 COHO AND 1 CHINOOK CAUGHT TODAY. VERY ODD FOR THIS TIME OF YR.
Wow,good numbers for sure !!! I'm sure theres a few guys here that wished they would of took you up on your offer
Awesome COPPER Sounds like you had fun and got into great numbers Great job and thanks for sharing Leechman
Me too. Except I hooked over forty by myself
its all about timing, nice to get on em at the right time.  Good job man!
Lets see some pictures Scotty.  Glad you had a good day.
GLAD TO SEE U GOT INTO A MESS OF FISH CONGRTAS, WE DID REALLY WELL SUN AND MON ASWELL SOME PICS AND MORE RELEASED WITH NONE CAUSE THE CAMERA DIED
TX GUYS. IS SURE HIT AND MISS BUT WHEN ITS ON ITS ON. 100 AN HR THATS GOOD. ILL HAVE TO WORK HARDER ON MY SKILLS. NO CAMERA THIS YR. BUSTED. MAYBE I GOT ONE FOR CHRISTMAS
sounds like a fish story to me... no pics... pics say  "40 fish" to me
Nice to hear from you again CC! Congrad on your outing, its definitely getting pretty cold outside, less people fishing. Stay warm and fish HARD!

hey scotty don't worry some of these guys just don't know what a 40 fish day feels like. when your are is ready to fall off by 9 in the morning ask gump about 52 in one morn and the gan last year and all the locals lest cause they got a little upset with us lol . some day guys you may to catch more then 2 fish in a day and know what your arm feels like.
since you don't get my joke and I know Scott you better..hmm how I should put this...
